cast.overview: On the brink of turning 30, a promising theater composer navigates love, friendship and the pressure to create something great before time runs out.
cast.title: tick, tick... BOOM!

details.biography: Robin de Jesús (born August 21, 1984) is an American film and theater actor of Puerto Rican descent. He is perhaps best known for playing the role of Sonny in the 2008 Broadway musical In The Heights, for which he received a Tony Award nomination for Best Featured Actor in a Musical. From 2010 to 2011, he was part of the revival cast of La Cage aux Folles.
details.name: Robin de Jesús
